title: Service Fabric Explorer Repository Reference
body: Service Fabric Explorer repository (Microsoft/service-fabric-explorer) provides web-based management interface for Service Fabric clusters. Contains Angular-based UI components, cluster visualization tools, application management features, and health monitoring dashboards. Essential for Service Fabric cluster administration and operational monitoring.
